      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's not really \"pain\" exactly, just a bit of a gritty, annoying feeling. and the vision is fine, nothing blurry. i really think it's just the screen strain because i've been working 10 hour shifts lately. honestly, if i just take some of those anti-inflammatory eye drops (the ones with steroids) instead of just lube, wouldn't that actually fix the redness faster? i have some left over from a prescription i used a year ago, is it safe to just use those for a couple days to clear this up?",
